OpenStreetMap Data License (ODbL 1.0)
=====================================

The datasets in this directory are extracts of OpenStreetMap (OSM) data
distributed by Geofabrik GmbH. Although Geofabrik provides the extraction
and packaging, the underlying data is created and maintained by the
OpenStreetMap community and is licensed under the Open Database License
(ODbL) 1.0.

You are free to:

  • Share: copy, distribute, and use the database.
  • Create: produce works from the database.
  • Adapt: modify, transform, and build upon the database.

As long as you:

  • Attribute: You must attribute “© OpenStreetMap contributors”.
  • Share-Alike: If you publicly use an adapted version of this database,
    or produce a derivative database, you must offer it under the ODbL 1.0.
  • Keep Open: If you redistribute the database, you must not impose
    additional restrictions that prevent others from exercising the ODbL rights.

Full license text:
<https://opendatacommons.org/licenses/odbl/1-0/>

Note on Geofabrik:
Geofabrik GmbH provides OSM extracts but does not impose any additional
license terms. The data remains governed solely by the ODbL 1.0.
